item.dc:creator: superadmin
item.content:encoded:
[vc_row padding_top_multiplier="6x" padding_bottom_multiplier="6x"][vc_column width="1/4"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][movedo_title heading_tag="div" heading="subtitle-text" align="center"]Capture moments since 2015[/movedo_title][movedo_title heading_tag="h1" heading="h2" custom_font_family="custom-font-1" align="center"]In photography there is a reality so subtle that it becomes more real than reality[/movedo_title][movedo_empty_space][movedo_title align="center"]the humanity of the moment[/movedo_title][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row bg_type="color" padding_bottom_multiplier="3x" bg_color="#f8f5ed"][vc_column column_custom_position="yes" position_top="minus-3x" width="1/2"][movedo_single_image image_mode="medium_large" image="24" grayscale_effect="grayscale-image"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/6"][/vc_column][vc_column column_custom_position="yes" position_top="2x" width="1/3"][movedo_single_image image_mode="medium_large" image="25" image_full_column="yes" image_column_space="125" align="left"][/vc_column][vc_column][movedo_empty_space][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/12"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][movedo_title margin_bottom="12"]How it all[/movedo_title][movedo_title heading="h2" custom_font_family="custom-font-1"]Began[/movedo_title][vc_column_text]A wonderful serenity has taken possession of my entire soul, like these sweet mornings of spring which I enjoy with my whole heart. I am alone, and feel the charm of existence in this spot, which was created for the bliss of souls like mine. I am so happy, my dear friend, so absorbed in the exquisite sense of mere tranquil existence, that I neglect my talents.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="5/12"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row padding_top_multiplier="3x" padding_bottom_multiplier="3x"][vc_column width="1/12"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][movedo_title margin_bottom="12"]Facts[/movedo_title][movedo_title heading="h2" custom_font_family="custom-font-1"]About me[/movedo_title][vc_column_text]1. Serenity has taken possession of my entire soul, like these
2. Sweet mornings of spring which I enjoy with my whole heart.
3. Lovely valley teems with vapour around me, and the meridian sun.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/6"][/vc_column][vc_column width="5/12"][vc_column_text]A wonderful serenity has taken possession of my entire soul, like these sweet mornings of spring which I enjoy with my whole heart. When, while the lovely valley teems with vapour around me, and the meridian sun strikes the upper surface of the impenetrable foliage of my trees, and but a few stray gleams steal into the inner sanctuary and something else.
I throw myself down among the tall grass by the trickling stream; and, as I lie close to the earth, a thousand unknown plants are noticed by me: when I hear the buzz of the little world among the stalks, and grow familiar with the countless indescribable forms of the insects and flies and something else, then I feel the presence of the Almighty, who formed us in his own image.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/12"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row bg_type="color" padding_top_multiplier="3x" padding_bottom_multiplier="3x" bg_color="#edf8ee"][vc_column width="1/12"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][movedo_title]Words from clients[/movedo_title][/vc_column][vc_column width="2/3" font_color="#000000"][movedo_testimonial text_style="quote-text"][/vc_column][/vc_row]
